snippet.title: Amber Heard's Double Life Is Completely Exposed
snippet.description:
In the 2000s, Amber Heard began making waves in Hollywood by starring in movies like "Never Back Down," "Pineapple Express," and "The Joneses." She’s carved out a respectable acting career over the years but lately, she’s been getting public attention for all the wrong reasons.

Heard's recent divorce from A-list "Pirates of the Caribbean" actor Johnny Depp has gotten messy to say the least. There have been allegations of assault, a filed restraining order, and conflicting evidence. Heard’s divorce has been tumultuous and oftentimes confusing which is why we’ve made a video exposing Amber Heard’s double life. Watch to find out!
